name: The Tower of Solitude
description:
A lone tower cutting through the forest while a storm is brewing. It's windy, raining and cold in the Mantiqueira Mountains.

This photo was minted to celebrate the milestone of 200 followers on Twitter. Thank you NFT community for your receptiveness and support!

Equipment: Sony Alpha A6500 + Sony E 18-135mm F/3.5-5.6 OSS
Location: Monte Verde, Minas Gerais, Brazil
